Kung ganoon nga,

00:34:02.770 --> 00:34:04.981
kapag kasama kita,

00:34:05.940 --> 00:34:08.067
ayos lang kung ayaw mong magsalita

00:34:08.151 --> 00:34:10.611
o hindi alam ang sasabihin.

00:34:12.071 --> 00:34:14.657
Sabihin mo lang sa akin na hindi ka malungkot.

00:34:20.538 --> 00:34:22.039
Paano ako magiging malungkot???

00:34:24.083 --> 00:34:25.543
kapag kasama kita?

