kanyang dating sarili,

00:44:39.031 --> 00:44:40.866
at nakalimutan na niya tayo,

00:44:42.493 --> 00:44:46.205
nakalimutan na rin niya

00:44:46.705 --> 00:44:48.832
ang kanyang pinakamasamang bangungot.

00:44:49.333 --> 00:44:50.417
Sa sandaling iyon,

00:44:50.501 --> 00:44:52.294
sa wakas ay naintindihan na rin namin.

00:44:52.377 --> 00:44:54.379
Hindi nabaliw si Hsiao-tung.

